PN,41607
SC,0007
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F416A1775139065
OL,3,CFirefighters vote in favour of strikes
OL,4,Cover planned cuts to fire service
OL,6,F"Our priority is, and will always
OL,7,Fremain, the safety of Oxfordshire's
OL,8,Fresidents and our firefighter
OL,9,Fcolleagues."
OL,11,FReporting History sees journalists
OL,12,Fjoin News At Ten anchor Tom Bradby to
